Package blf.grammar

Class BcqlUtilBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • blf.grammar.BcqlUtilBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BcqlUtilListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    public class BcqlUtilBaseListener
extends Object
implements BcqlUtilListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of BcqlUtilListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
